## THE PROBLEM: Digital Memory Is Fragile

Modern memory systems fail because they are **designed to be rewritten**:

- Cloud storage gets â€œoptimizedâ€ (corrupted)
- Algorithms decide what you see
- Platforms reset, accounts vanish
